---
layout: base.njk
title: Takes | Morgan Guinyard
description: Hot takes and cold ones too — opinions, observations, and the occasional rant from Morgan Guinyard.
---

<section class="blog-hero">
    <h1>hot takes (cold ones too)</h1>
    <p>opinions, observations, and the occasional rant</p>
</section>

<section class="info-section">
    {% if collections.posts and collections.posts.length %}
    <div class="latest-posts">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
        <div class="card blog-post-card">
            <div class="blog-post-card-text">
                <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
                {% if post.data.description %}<p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
                <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="blog-coming-soon">
        <p>posts incoming. check back soon.</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
</section>
